title: Thai-inspired Crispy Duck & Arugula Salad
summary: Thai-inspired Crispy Duck & Arugula Salad is a dairy free main course. One serving contains 651 calories, 77g of protein, and 32g of fat. This recipe serves 5. For $3.63 per serving, this recipe covers 26% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. 14 people have made this recipe and would make it again. Head to the store and pick up kohlrabi bulbs, cheater duck confit legs, everyday paleo's thai “no peanut” sauce, and a few other things to make it today. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 86%. This score is outstanding.
